    </div>

    <div class="byline">
      <div class="byline__profile-image">C</div>
      <div class="byline__attribution">
        by <a href="/">Contributor-pseudonym</a> <time>Jul 23, 2019</time>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="underlined">Ut volutpat enimve mattis dignissim</h2>
    <p>
      Cras condimentum rutrum nibh, et vulputate augue cursus non. Donec at
      mollis mi. Ut id turpis in orci sagittis gravida et et massa. Nunc
      molestie tur.
